This paper discusses the responsible development of AI, which is a key topic in the field of AI (cs.AI). It also touches upon issues related to cybersecurity (cs.CY) and collective action problems (cs.CR). The strategies proposed in the paper involve cooperation and coordination among AI companies, which falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI). Finally, the paper discusses the incentives and competitive pressures that AI companies face, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG).
